  4,98,Except the weak among men and women and children who cannot evade and they are not directed to a way
  4,99,And perhaps God excuses them. God is pardoning and forgiving
  4,100,"And whoever migrates in God's way finds many refuge and plenty on the earth. And whoever leaves his house migrating for God and His messenger, then the death reaches him (and he dies), then his reward has fallen upon God. And God is forgiving and merciful"
  4,101,When you travel throughout the earth there is no blame on you if you shorten your mandatory prayer if you are afraid that those who disbelieved may harm you. Indeed the disbelievers are your obvious enemy